    {
      "id": "94",
      "name": "Media",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Trailers and Story Teasers",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Perilous Trail Event Cutscene Animation: \"Moment of Life or Death\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/01/237301566/5f3df653c1e823be8492f2fe8d0c7dfe_2375227229398725591.jpg"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "June 5, 2022",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Many years ago, the adeptus Sea Gazer made good friends with a thaumaturge. Emulating the story of adepti and mortal kindred spirits recorded in ancient texts, he gave the mortal his treasured device to aid his friend in battle.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "He said: \"Look, my friend. This contraption is rather intriguing. If you and I activate it, one can move the heavens and shake the earth.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Such is how the world works. What one may fail to do, two may succeed.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "I have spent much time gazing at the sea in leisure and have seldom exerted myself, but it is my pleasure to aid others in need.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The battle ahead is fraught with peril. Millennia later, both you and I may linger in this world no more. When the time comes, someone can return this device to the mountains, which will serve as testament to our friendship.\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Thus did the catalyst find its way into mortal homes and stayed in their hands until...",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "\"Endless Suffering\" Short Trailer",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/30/35428890/55e2e01841797ea02b449a87a46ae62c_6730330635463270557.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "January 21, 2023",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "A new year brings with it new opportunities, dear friends, and good fortune.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "On this night filled with a vibrant spectrum of lights, there's more than just lanterns in Liyue Harbor. Listen, for a brilliant resonance of celestial melodies rings in the air.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
